Avril Lavigne is the upcoming self-titled fifth studio album by Canadian singer-songwriter Avril Lavigne. The album is scheduled to be released on 1 November 2013 by Epic Records and is the follow-up to her fourth studio album, Goodbye Lullaby (2011).
